==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''quarto'' for the fourth time

===Noun===
'''quarto'''
# A size of paper 10 by 8 inches (254mm x 203mm).
# A book of a size between 11 and 13 inches tall. Intermediate in size between [[octavo]] and [[folio]]. Abbreviated [[4to]].

